page.title: 19THE LIFE OF AN 11 YEAR OLD
page.content: My name is Daniel Cant and I live at 2 Hungate Road. I like football and watching Dallas. I like to wear a tie and lots of fashionable clothes. In my family I have a Mum and a Dad and a big sister that goes to the Senior School and she is a prefect. My mum works on a farm and my Dad is a contractor. I have only one pet and she is a cat. She is a breed of tabby and she has a lot of colours on her coat and she is called Tina. My house is on an estate and it is new and it is made of bricks. I have a big garden and it has lots of flowers in the spring and summer. In the house is a big staircase and three bedrooms and a sittingroom and a bathroom and a kitchen. In my bedroom I have a Man Utd wallpaper and a Man Utd quilt and curtains.
